accessibility.text: Rozendaal founded BYOB (Bring Your Own Beamer), an open source exhibition concept.
The idea is that anyone can create an exhibition of media art without any budget.
\"Find a space, Invite many artists, Ask them to bring their projector\".
Since its beginning in 2010, more than 150 BYOB events were organized around the world. In 2011, BYOB was the theme of the II Internet Pavilion for the Venice Biennale.
